data.description: Great starter home! This 2-bedroom 1 bath home has been nicely updated. The kitchen has white shaker cabinets and granite counter tops. There is tile throughout, newer appliances and the roof was re-shingled in 2020. The spacious laundry room has lots of cabinets and the washer and dryer are included. Walk out the sliding glass doors onto the large, screened Lanai overlooking the canal. This home would be ideal for a first-time home buyer or rental income. Great location, close to schools, Dr offices, shopping, and restaurants. This will go fast!!
